words: All BTC .:. News: Using Bitcoin Mixer for the payments Using Bitcoin Mixer for the payments (2024.01.19) About two weeks ago we started using Bitcoin mixers to send transfers to customers. Some were happy about it and some were upset. Using Bitcoin mixers is very safe and makes the Bitcoin untraceable, but it can take up to three weeks to deliver. Some directories give us bad reviews without asking us for a reason. Some customers who commented badly in some places and after receiving bitcoin did not try to correct their commentss. >> Remember that you can announce after the payment that you do not need a bitcoin mixer to transfer bitcoins quickly into your wallet.
